      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy verification was performed via the GCI study documented in the VerificationActivity. Observed order is consistent with second-order discretisation. However, manufactured-solution verification was not completed, limiting the achieved level to 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
