      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model was selected based on prior literature for rotating machinery. Sensitivity analysis comparing SST to RSM was performed at one operating point only. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model was used without independent calibration against VAD-specific data. Achieved level 2."
