    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factors achieving levels below required thresholds, the assessment team accepted the package on the basis that the NIH predictions remain below the absolute clinical threshold across all five operating points and that Monte Carlo UQ confirms robustness of this conclusion. The GCI mesh independence study documented in the VerificationActivity demonstrates acceptable numerical discretization error. Remaining gaps are acknowledged and will be addressed in a follow-on assessment prior to PMA submission.",
